							<body  ><div class="section"><p class="BillDebate"><strong>IMPREST SUPPLY (SECOND FOR 2016/17) BILL</strong></p><p class="SubDebate"><strong>Third Reading</strong></p><p class="Speech"><a name="time_20160816 17:47:28" ></a><strong>Hon BILL ENGLISH (Minister of Finance)</strong>: I move, <em>That the Imprest Supply (Second for 2016/17) Bill be now read a third time</em>. </p><p class="IndentMarginalone">Bill read a third time.</p></div></body>
